%% Logical architecture (Mermaid)
graph TD
  subgraph Edge
    User[User (Web / Mobile)] -->|HTTPS| CDN[CDN / Edge]
  end

  subgraph App
    CDN --> Frontend[Frontend (Next.js / Static)]
    Frontend --> API[API Gateway / FastAPI]
    API --> Auth[Auth Service (JWT / OAuth)]
    API --> Services[Backend Services (domain modules)]
    Services --> Postgres[(Postgres DB)]
    Services --> Redis[(Redis cache)]
    Services --> Queue[(Task queue / Celery / RabbitMQ)]
    Services --> Storage[(Object storage / S3-compatible)]
    Services -->|events| EventBus[(Event Bus / PubSub)]
  end

  Auth --> Postgres
  Observability[(Prometheus / Grafana / Loki)] <-- Services
  Observability <-- API
  CI[CI/CD] -->|deploy| Cluster[Kubernetes / Container Apps]
